DNS stand for domain name system
1) task of Domain Hierarchy 
1.1 What is the maximum length of a subdomain?
ans) 63
1.2) Which of the following characters cannot be used in a subdomain ( 3 b _ - )?
ans) -
What is the maximum length of a domain name? ans) 253
What type of TLD is .co.uk? ans) ccTLD
2) task of RECORD TYPE
2.1) What type of record would be used to advise where to send email?
ans) MX
2.2) What type of record handles IPv6 addresses? ans) AAAA
3) task of making a request 
3.1) What field specifies how long a DNS record should be cached for? ans) TTL
3.2) What type of DNS Server is usually provided by your ISP? ans) recursive
3.3) What type of server holds all the records for a domain? ans) authoritative
4) practical
4.1) What is the CNAME of shop.website.thm? ans) shops.myshopify.com
4.2) What is the value of the TXT record of website.thm? ans) THM{7012BBA60997F35A9516C2E16D2944FF}
4.3) What is the numerical priority value for the MX record? ans) 30
4.4) What is the IP address for the A record of www.website.thm? ans) 10.10.10.10
